  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Moredo_Rogare.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/ca/Moredo_Rogare.png/350px-Moredo_Rogare.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/ca/Moredo_Rogare.png/525px-Moredo_Rogare.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/ca/Moredo_Rogare.png/700px-Moredo_Rogare.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Moredo_Rogare.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Truth, wielded by <a href=\"/index.php/Moredo_Rogare\" title=\"Moredo Rogare\">Moredo Rogare</a></div></div></div>\n<p><b>Truth</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_steel\" title=\"Valyrian steel\">Valyrian steel</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Longsword\" title=\"Longsword\">longsword</a> carried by <a href=\"/index.php/Moredo_Rogare\" title=\"Moredo Rogare\">Moredo Rogare</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lysene</a> noble from the wealthy banking <a href=\"/index.php/Rogare_family\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Rogare family\">Rogare family</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_quarrelsome_daughters:_myr.2C_lys.2C_and_tyrosh.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_quarrelsome_daughters:_myr.2C_lys.2C_and_tyrosh.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Truth_(sword)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Refe